reviewText: Love love love, this show! Watch all the time! Clean family fun!
Would recommend to friends. Enjoyed watching this family very much. Something the whole family can watch and enjoy all together.

All dvd's worked great.  The episodes were quite funny and so down to earth with wholesome humor and entertainment.  I've enjoyed watching them and viewing over again.  I enjoyed them so much that I bought Season 4 too.
This was a gift for the hubby and he loves it! He's a hunter and the comedy in the show totally suits his humor. We also appreciate the family values in the show
Duck Dynasty is fun to watch when you are a redneck. Good old fashion fun. It's nice to see a different perspective on life.

I've been watching this series since its inception but my brother, who has neither cable nor internet, hasn't see it. I purchased this set for him for Christmas and he LOVES IT! Watched all of Season One in one sitting! These guys are hilarious!
